  "name": "Admin Forms - Re-activating an outlet",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"admin-forms-re-activating-an-outlet\">Admin Forms - Re-activating an outlet</h1>\n<p><span><span>This article explains how to re-activate a previously de-activated outlet/unmanned warehouse in an existing clients Retail Express database.</span></span></p>\n<p><span>Re-Enabling the Licence</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"364\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nHIa2EAG.png\" width=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 364px; width: 500px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nHIa2EAG.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nHIa2EAG.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nHIa2EAG.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nHIa2EAG.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nHIa2EAG.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nHIa2EAG.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000nHIa2EAG.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Login to clients Retail Express</p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>Settings &gt; Locations / Outlets &gt; Outlets</strong></p>\n<p>3. Select the relevant outlet and click the blue Edit button which will populate the <strong>Outlet Details</strong> section in the top half of the screen</p>\n<p>4. Tick the <em>Enabled </em>checkbox</p>\n<p>5. Click <strong>Save</strong></p>\n<p>6. Repeat as necessary if they are re-activating more than one licence</p>\n<p><span>Zoho Subscription - Updating Monthly Hosting</span></p>\n<p>1. Login to <em>Zoho Subscriptions</em></p>\n<p>2. Search for clients monthly subscription</p>\n<p>3. Edit subscription to update the quantity field for the number of outlets</p>\n<p>4. Click <strong>Save</strong></p>\n<p>5. When it asks if you want this to be effective immediately or next term - say<strong> Immediately</strong> and it will automatically generate a pro-rata invoice</p>\n<p>5. Add comment stating \"Reactivation of outlet xxx [Zendesk Ticket #] pro-rata invoice raised\"</p>\n<p>6. If an Ezypay customer login to Ezypay to update their ongoing monthly fees from the next monthly invoice cycle including the pro-rata amount for the next invoice</p>\n<p><span>Zendesk - Sending the email </span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"134\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nHIaCEAW.png\" width=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 134px; width: 500px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nHIaCEAW.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nHIaCEAW.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nHIaCEAW.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nHIaCEAW.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nHIaCEAW.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nHIaCEAW.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000nHIaCEAW.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Update the email address to be the one on the completed online form in original ticket</p>\n<p>3. Select the macro <strong>Forms &gt; Re-activate an Outlet - completed</strong></p>\n<p>5. Submit the ticket as <strong>Solved</strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
